<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>نخلة بابل للسياحة والسفر | Palm of Babylon</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Tajawal:wght@400;500;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

        :root {
            --primary-blue: #1a5f9e;
            --dark-blue: #0d3a5c;
            --light-blue: #e8f4fc;
            --orange: #f26522;
            --white: #ffffff;
            --dark: #1a1a1a;
            --gray: #666666;
            --whatsapp: #25d366;
            --bg-primary: #ffffff;
            --bg-secondary: #f8f9fa;
            --bg-hero: linear-gradient(135deg, #e8f4fc 0%, #ffffff 100%);
            --text-primary: #1a1a1a;
            --text-secondary: #666666;
            --card-bg: #ffffff;
            --card-border: #eee;
            --footer-bg: #1a1a1a;
            --header-bg: #ffffff;
            --header-shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
        }

        [data-theme="dark"] {
            --bg-primary: #0f172a;
            --bg-secondary: #1e293b;
            --bg-hero: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d3a5c 0%, #0f172a 100%);
            --text-primary: #f1f5f9;
            --text-secondary: #94a3b8;
            --card-bg: #1e293b;
            --card-border: #334155;
            --footer-bg: #020617;
            --header-bg: #0f172a;
            --header-shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Tajawal', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            background: var(--bg-primary);
            overflow-x: hidden;
            transition: background 0.3s, color 0.3s;
        }

        .theme-toggle {
            position: fixed;
            top: 100px;
            left: 20px;
            z-index: 999;
            background: var(--orange);
            border: none;
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(242, 101, 34, 0.4);
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .theme-toggle:hover { transform: scale(1.1); }
        [data-theme="dark"] .theme-toggle { background: #fbbf24; }
        .theme-toggle .sun { display: none; }
        [data-theme="dark"] .theme-toggle .sun { display: block; }
        [data-theme="dark"] .theme-toggle .moon { display: none; }

        header {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            width: 100%;
            background: var(--header-bg);
            box-shadow: var(--header-shadow);
            z-index: 1000;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .nav-container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0.5rem 2rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .logo-img {
            height: 65px;
            width: auto;
            object-fit: contain;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        [data-theme="dark"] .logo-img {
            filter: brightness(1.3) contrast(1.1);
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 2.5rem;
            list-style: none;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            position: relative;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--primary-blue); }

        .nav-links a::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -5px;
            right: 0;
            width: 0;
            height: 3px;
            background: var(--orange);
            border-radius: 2px;
            transition: width 0.3s;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover::after { width: 100%; }

        .cta-btn {
            background: var(--orange);
            color: var(--white) !important;
            padding: 0.6rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 25px;
            transition: all 0.3s !important;
        }

        .cta-btn:hover { background: var(--primary-blue); transform: translateY(-2px); }
        .cta-btn::after { display: none !important; }

        .mobile-menu {
            display: none;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            color: var(--primary-blue);
            cursor: pointer;
            background: none;
            border: none;
            padding: 5px;
            z-index: 1001;
        }

        .nav-overlay {
            display: none;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            z-index: 998;
        }

        .nav-overlay.active { display: block; }

        .hero {
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: var(--bg-hero);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding-top: 100px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .hero::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            left: -20%;
            width: 800px;
            height: 800px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(26,95,158,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        [data-theme="dark"] .hero::before {
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(242,101,34,0.05) 0%, transparent 70%);
        }

        .hero-container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 2rem;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 4rem;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .hero-content {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }

        .hero-logo-main {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 320px;
            height: auto;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            object-fit: contain;
        }

        [data-theme="dark"] .hero-logo-main {
            filter: brightness(1.3) contrast(1.1);
        }

        .hero-content h1 {
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            line-height: 1.3;
            color: var(--dark-blue);
        }

        [data-theme="dark"] .hero-content h1 { color: #60a5fa; }
        .hero-content h1 span { color: var(--orange); }

        .hero-content p {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            max-width: 500px;
        }

        .hero-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: var(--primary-blue);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: var(--dark-blue);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(26,95,158,0.3);
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background: transparent;
            color: var(--primary-blue);
            padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            border: 2px solid var(--primary-blue);
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        [data-theme="dark"] .btn-secondary { color: #60a5fa; border-color: #60a5fa; }
        .btn-secondary:hover { background: var(--primary-blue); color: var(--white); }
        [data-theme="dark"] .btn-secondary:hover { background: #60a5fa; color: #0f172a; }

        .hero-image { position: relative; }

        .hero-image img {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }

        .floating-card {
            position: absolute;
            background: var(--card-bg);
            padding: 1.2rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .card-1 { top: 20%; left: -30px; animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite; }
        .card-2 { bottom: 15%; right: -20px; animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite 0.5s; }

        .floating-card h4 { color: var(--orange); font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 800; }
        .floating-card p { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.9rem; }

        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-15px); }
        }

        .animate-on-scroll {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(30px);
            transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease;
        }

        .animate-on-scroll.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

        .stats { background: var(--primary-blue); padding: 4rem 2rem; }

        .stats-container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
            gap: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .stat-item h3 { color: var(--orange); font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 800; }
        .stat-item p { color: var(--white); font-size: 1.1rem; margin-top: 0.5rem; }

        .services { padding: 6rem 2rem; background: var(--bg-primary); }

        .section-header {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto 4rem;
        }

        .section-header h2 { font-size: 2.5rem; color: var(--dark-blue); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        [data-theme="dark"] .section-header h2 { color: #60a5fa; }
        .section-header h2 span { color: var(--orange); }
        .section-header p { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 1.1rem; }

        .services-grid {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .service-card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            padding: 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
        }

        .service-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
            border-color: var(--primary-blue);
        }

        .service-icon {
            width: 90px;
            height: 90px;
            background: var(--light-blue);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        [data-theme="dark"] .service-icon { background: rgba(26, 95, 158, 0.2); }
        .service-card:hover .service-icon { background: var(--primary-blue); }
        .service-card h3 { color: var(--text-primary); font-size: 1.4rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        .service-card p { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.95rem; }

        .destinations { padding: 6rem 2rem; background: var(--bg-secondary); }

        .destinations-grid {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }

        .destination-card {
            position: relative;
            border-radius: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
            height: 380px;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }

        .destination-card img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: transform 0.5s;
        }

        .destination-card:hover img { transform: scale(1.1); }

        .destination-overlay {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
            padding: 2rem 1.5rem 1.5rem;
            background: linear-gradient(transparent 0%, rgba(13,58,92,0.95) 100%);
            color: var(--white);
        }

        .destination-overlay h4 { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 800; }

        .duration-tag {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 0.4rem 0.9rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.3rem;
        }

        .why-us { padding: 6rem 2rem; background: var(--bg-primary); }

        .why-container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 5rem;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .why-image { position: relative; }

        .why-image img {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
        }

        .experience-badge {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -20px;
            left: -20px;
            background: var(--orange);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(242, 101, 34, 0.3);
        }

        .experience-badge h4 { font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 800; }
        .experience-badge p { font-size: 1rem; }

        .why-content h2 { font-size: 2.5rem; color: var(--dark-blue); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
        [data-theme="dark"] .why-content h2 { color: #60a5fa; }
        .why-content h2 span { color: var(--orange); }
        .why-content > p { color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 2rem; font-size: 1.05rem; }
        .why-list { list-style: none; }

        .why-list li {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .check-icon {
            width: 30px;
            height: 30px;
            min-width: 30px;
            background: var(--light-blue);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: var(--primary-blue);
            font-weight: bold;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            margin-top: 3px;
        }

        [data-theme="dark"] .check-icon { background: rgba(26, 95, 158, 0.2); color: #60a5fa; }
        .why-list h4 { color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
        .why-list p { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.95rem; }

        .contact {
            padding: 6rem 2rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--dark-blue) 0%, var(--primary-blue) 100%);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        [data-theme="dark"] .contact { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e3a5f 100%); }

        .contact::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0; right: 0;
            width: 400px; height: 400px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(242,101,34,0.15) 0%, transparent 70%);
        }

        .contact-container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 4rem;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .contact-info h2 { color: var(--white); font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
        .contact-info h2 span { color: var(--orange); }
        .contact-info > p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); margin-bottom: 2.5rem; font-size: 1.05rem; }

        .contact-details { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; }

        .contact-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 1rem;
            color: var(--white);
        }

        .contact-icon {
            width: 55px;
            height: 55px;
            min-width: 55px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            border-radius: 15px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .contact-item:hover .contact-icon { background: var(--orange); }
        .contact-text h4 { font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
        .contact-text p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.6; }

        .phone-row {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.8rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .phone-link {
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1rem;
            direction: ltr;
            display: inline-block;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        .phone-link:hover { color: var(--orange); }

        .whatsapp-btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.4rem;
            background: var(--whatsapp);
            color: var(--white) !important;
            padding: 0.4rem 0.9rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .whatsapp-btn:hover { transform: scale(1.05); box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(37, 211, 102, 0.3); }

        .location-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: var(--orange);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .map-link {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.4rem;
            color: var(--orange);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-top: 0.3rem;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .map-link:hover { color: #fff; text-decoration: underline; }

        .contact-form {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            padding: 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }

        .contact-form h3 { color: var(--dark-blue); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-size: 1.5rem; }
        [data-theme="dark"] .contact-form h3 { color: #60a5fa; }

        .form-group { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
        .form-group label { display: block; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: var(--text-primary); font-weight: 500; }

        .form-group input,
        .form-group textarea,
        .form-group select {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 1rem;
            border: 2px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-family: 'Tajawal', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: border-color 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
            background: var(--bg-primary);
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        .form-group input:focus,
        .form-group textarea:focus,
        .form-group select:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: var(--primary-blue);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(26, 95, 158, 0.15);
        }

        .form-group textarea { min-height: 120px; resize: vertical; }
        .form-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem; }

        .custom-select-wrapper { position: relative; }

        .custom-select-trigger {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0.85rem 1rem;
            border: 2px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-family: 'Tajawal', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1rem;
            background: var(--bg-primary);
            color: var(--text-primary);
            cursor: pointer;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.8rem;
            transition: border-color 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
            user-select: none;
            min-height: 54px;
        }

        .custom-select-trigger:hover { border-color: var(--primary-blue); }

        .custom-select-trigger.open {
            border-color: var(--primary-blue);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(26, 95, 158, 0.15);
            border-radius: 12px 12px 0 0;
        }

        .custom-select-trigger.error { border-color: #ef4444 !important; }

        .custom-select-trigger .trigger-img {
            width: 40px; height: 30px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            object-fit: cover;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }

        .custom-select-trigger .trigger-text { flex: 1; }
        .custom-select-trigger .trigger-placeholder { color: var(--text-secondary); }

        .custom-select-trigger .trigger-arrow {
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            transition: transform 0.3s;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .custom-select-trigger.open .trigger-arrow { transform: rotate(180deg); }

        .custom-select-dropdown {
            position: absolute;
            top: 100%; left: 0; right: 0;
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border: 2px solid var(--primary-blue);
            border-top: none;
            border-radius: 0 0 12px 12px;
            max-height: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
            z-index: 100;
            transition: max-height 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }

        .custom-select-dropdown.open { max-height: 400px; overflow-y: auto; }

        .custom-option {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.8rem;
            padding: 0.7rem 1rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.2s;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--card-border);
        }

        .custom-option:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
        .custom-option:hover { background: var(--light-blue); }
        [data-theme="dark"] .custom-option:hover { background: rgba(26, 95, 158, 0.2); }
        .custom-option.selected { background: rgba(26, 95, 158, 0.1); }

        .custom-option .option-img {
            width: 55px; height: 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            object-fit: cover;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }

        .custom-option:hover .option-img { transform: scale(1.05); }
        .custom-option .option-info { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }
        .custom-option .option-name { font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-primary); font-size: 0.95rem; }
        .custom-option .option-duration { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-secondary); }
        .custom-option.no-img { padding: 0.9rem 1rem; }
        .custom-option.no-img .option-icon { font-size: 1.3rem; width: 40px; text-align: center; flex-shrink: 0; }

        .destination-preview {
            margin-top: 0.8rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            max-height: 0;
            opacity: 0;
            transition: max-height 0.4s ease, opacity 0.3s ease;
        }

        .destination-preview.show { max-height: 220px; opacity: 1; }

        .destination-preview .preview-card {
            position: relative;
            height: 160px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }

        .destination-preview .preview-card img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }

        .destination-preview .preview-overlay {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
            padding: 1rem;
            background: linear-gradient(transparent 0%, rgba(13,58,92,0.9) 100%);
            color: white;
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-end;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .destination-preview .preview-name { font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.1rem; }

        .submit-btn {
            width: 100%;
            background: var(--orange);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 1rem;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-family: 'Tajawal', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .submit-btn:hover { background: var(--dark-blue); transform: translateY(-2px); }

        .form-success { display: none; text-align: center; padding: 2rem; }
        .form-success.show { display: block; }
        .form-success .success-icon { font-size: 4rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        .form-success h4 { color: var(--primary-blue); font-size: 1.3rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
        [data-theme="dark"] .form-success h4 { color: #60a5fa; }
        .form-success p { color: var(--text-secondary); }

        .floating-whatsapp { position: fixed; bottom: 25px; left: 25px; z-index: 999; }

        .floating-whatsapp a {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.6rem;
            background: var(--whatsapp);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1rem;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(37, 211, 102, 0.4);
            transition: all 0.3s;
            animation: pulse-whatsapp 2s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes pulse-whatsapp {
            0% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(37, 211, 102, 0.4); }
            70% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 15px rgba(37, 211, 102, 0); }
            100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(37, 211, 102, 0); }
        }

        .floating-whatsapp a:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); animation: none; }
        .floating-whatsapp .wa-icon { font-size: 1.5rem; }

        footer {
            background: var(--footer-bg);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 4rem 2rem 2rem;
        }

        .footer-container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 3rem;
        }

        .footer-brand .logo-footer {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .footer-logo-img {
            height: 80px;
            width: auto;
            object-fit: contain;
            filter: brightness(0) invert(1);
        }

        .footer-brand > p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
        .footer-contact { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }

        .footer-contact-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 0.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        .footer-contact-item .fc-icon { color: var(--orange); flex-shrink: 0; width: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .footer-phone { direction: ltr; display: inline-block; }

        .social-links { display: flex; gap: 1rem; }

        .social-links a {
            width: 45px; height: 45px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            border-radius: 12px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: var(--white);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        .social-links a:hover { background: var(--orange); transform: translateY(-3px); }

        .footer-links h4 { color: var(--orange); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-size: 1.2rem; }
        .footer-links ul { list-style: none; }
        .footer-links li { margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }
        .footer-links a { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.3s; }
        .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--orange); }

        .footer-bottom {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 3rem auto 0;
            padding-top: 2rem;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            text-align: center;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
        }

        .back-to-top {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 25px;
            right: 25px;
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            background: var(--primary-blue);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            z-index: 999;
            opacity: 0;
            visibility: hidden;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(26, 95, 158, 0.3);
        }

        .back-to-top.visible { opacity: 1; visibility: visible; }
        .back-to-top:hover { background: var(--dark-blue); transform: translateY(-3px); }

        @media (max-width: 1024px) {
            .hero-container, .why-container, .contact-container { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .hero-image { order: -1; }
            .hero-logo-main { max-width: 280px; }
            .services-grid, .destinations-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
            .stats-container { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
            .footer-container { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .theme-toggle { top: 90px; left: 15px; width: 45px; height: 45px; font-size: 1.3rem; }

            .nav-links {
                display: none;
                position: absolute;
                top: 100%; left: 0; right: 0;
                background: var(--header-bg);
                flex-direction: column;
                padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
                box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
                gap: 0;
                border-top: 2px solid var(--orange);
            }

            .nav-links.active { display: flex; }
            .nav-links li { padding: 0.8rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--card-border); }
            .nav-links li:last-child { border-bottom: none; padding-top: 1rem; }
            .nav-links a { display: block; font-size: 1.1rem; }
            .nav-links a::after { display: none; }
            .mobile-menu { display: block; }
            .hero { padding-top: 90px; }
            .hero-content h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
            .hero-logo-main { max-width: 220px; }
            .services-grid, .destinations-grid, .stats-container { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .footer-container { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .floating-card { display: none; }
            .experience-badge { left: 20px; bottom: 20px; padding: 1.5rem; }
            .experience-badge h4 { font-size: 2rem; }
            .floating-whatsapp { bottom: 20px; left: 20px; }
            .floating-whatsapp a { padding: 0.9rem; border-radius: 50%; }
            .floating-whatsapp .whatsapp-text { display: none; }
            .destination-card { height: 320px; }
            .logo-img { height: 50px; }
            .section-header h2 { font-size: 2rem; }
            .form-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .back-to-top { bottom: 80px; right: 15px; width: 45px; height: 45px; }
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .hero-content h1 { font-size: 1.7rem; }
            .hero-content p { font-size: 1.05rem; }
            .btn-primary, .btn-secondary { padding: 0.85rem 1.8rem; font-size: 1rem; }
            .hero-buttons { flex-direction: column; align-items: stretch; text-align: center; }
            .contact-form { padding: 1.5rem; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <button class="theme-toggle" id="themeToggle" title="تبديل الوضع">
        <span class="moon">🌙</span>
        <span class="sun">☀️</span>
    </button>

    <button class="back-to-top" id="backToTop" title="العودة للأعلى">↑</button>

    <header id="mainHeader">
        <nav class="nav-container">
            <a href="#home" class="logo">
                <img src="logo.png" alt="نخلة بابل" class="logo-img">
            </a>
            <ul class="nav-links" id="navLinks">
                <li><a href="#home">الرئيسية</a></li>
                <li><a href="#services">خدماتنا</a></li>
                <li><a href="#destinations">الوجهات</a></li>
                <li><a href="#about">من نحن</a></li>
                <li><a href="#contact" class="cta-btn">احجز الآن</a></li>
            </ul>
            <button class="mobile-menu" id="mobileMenu">☰</button>
        </nav>
        <div class="nav-overlay" id="navOverlay"></div>
    </header>

    <section class="hero" id="home">
        <div class="hero-container">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <img src="logo.png" alt="نخلة بابل للسياحة والسفر" class="hero-logo-main">
                <h1>اكتشف العالم مع <span>نخلة بابل</span></h1>
                <p>نحن نصنع رحلات لا تُنسى. من حجز تذاكر الطيران إلى ترتيب أفضل الفنادق والجولات السياحية، نحن معك في كل خطوة.</p>
                <div class="hero-buttons">
                    <a href="#destinations" class="btn-primary">استكشف الوجهات ←</a>
                    <a href="#contact" class="btn-secondary">تواصل معنا</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-image">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1436491865332-7a61a109cc05?w=600&q=80" alt="سفر وسياحة">
                <div class="floating-card card-1">
                    <h4>+5000</h4>
                    <p>عميل سعيد</p>
                </div>
                <div class="floating-card card-2">
                    <h4>+50</h4>
                    <p>وجهة حول العالم</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="stats">
        <div class="stats-container">
            <div class="stat-item animate-on-scroll">
                <h3><span class="counter" data-target="15">0</span>+</h3>
                <p>سنة خبرة</p>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-item animate-on-scroll">
                <h3><span class="counter" data-target="5000">0</span>+</h3>
                <p>عميل سعيد</p>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-item animate-on-scroll">
                <h3><span class="counter" data-target="50">0</span>+</h3>
                <p>وجهة سياحية</p>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-item animate-on-scroll">
                <h3>24/7</h3>
                <p>دعم مخصص</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="services" id="services">
        <div class="section-header animate-on-scroll">
            <h2>خدماتنا <span>المتميزة</span></h2>
            <p>نقدم لك مجموعة شاملة من خدمات السفر والسياحة لتجربة سلسة ومريحة</p>
        </div>
        <div class="services-grid">
            <div class="service-card animate-on-scroll">
                <div class="service-icon"><span>✈️</span></div>
                <h3>حجز تذاكر الطيران</h3>
                <p>أفضل الأسعار على تذاكر الطيران لجميع الوجهات العالمية مع خيارات مرنة للتعديل والإلغاء</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service-card animate-on-scroll">
                <div class="service-icon"><span>🏨</span></div>
                <h3>حجز الفنادق</h3>
                <p>اختيار واسع من الفنادق الفاخرة والاقتصادية مع تأكيد فوري وضمان أفضل سعر</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service-card animate-on-scroll">
                <div class="service-icon"><span>🕌</span></div>
                <h3>العمرة والزيارة</h3>
                <p>باقات متكاملة لأداء العمرة والزيارة تشمل الإقامة والنقل والخدمات اللوجستية</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service-card animate-on-scroll">
                <div class="service-icon"><span>🎫</span></div>
                <h3>التأشيرات السياحية</h3>
                <p>إنجاز معاملات التأشيرات بسرعة وكفاءة مع متابعة مستمرة لحالة الطلب</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service-card animate-on-scroll">
                <div class="service-icon"><span>🚗</span></div>
                <h3>المواصلات والنقل</h3>
                <p>خدمات نقل مريحة من وإلى المطار، بالإضافة إلى تأجير السيارات في الوجهة</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service-card animate-on-scroll">
                <div class="service-icon"><span>🎯</span></div>
                <h3>الجولات السياحية</h3>
                <p>برامج سياحية منظمة مع مرشدين محترفين لاستكشاف أجمل المعالم العالمية</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="destinations" id="destinations">
        <div class="section-header animate-on-scroll">
            <h2>وجهاتنا <span>المميزة</span></h2>
            <p>اختر من بين أفضل العروض السياحية المُعدة خصيصاً لك</p>
        </div>
        <div class="destinations-grid">
            <div class="destination-card animate-on-scroll">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1537996194471-e657df975ab4?w=400&q=80" alt="فيزا بالي">
                <div class="destination-overlay">
                    <h4>فيزا بالي</h4>
                    <span class="duration-tag">⏱ 10-15 يوم عمل</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="destination-card animate-on-scroll">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1512453979798-5ea266f8880c?w=400&q=80" alt="فيزا قطر">
                <div class="destination-overlay">
                    <h4>فيزا قطر</h4>
                    <span class="duration-tag">⏱ 5-15 يوم عمل</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="destination-card animate-on-scroll">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1565008447742-97f6f38c985c?w=400&q=80" alt="فيزا جورجيا">
                <div class="destination-overlay">
                    <h4>فيزا جورجيا</h4>
                    <span class="duration-tag">⏱ 10-15 يوم عمل</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="destination-card animate-on-scroll">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1572252009286-268acec5ca0a?w=400&q=80" alt="موافقة مصر">
                <div class="destination-overlay">
                    <h4>موافقة مصر</h4>
                    <span class="duration-tag">⏱ 7-14 يوم عمل</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="destination-card animate-on-scroll">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1552465011-b4e21bf6e79a?w=400&q=80" alt="تأشيرة تايلند">
                <div class="destination-overlay">
                    <h4>تأشيرة تايلند</h4>
                    <span class="duration-tag">⏱ 72 ساعة عمل</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="destination-card animate-on-scroll">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518684079-3c830dcef090?w=400&q=80" alt="تأشيرة دبي">
                <div class="destination-overlay">
                    <h4>تأشيرة دبي</h4>
                    <span class="duration-tag">⏱ 72 ساعة عمل</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="why-us" id="about">
        <div class="why-container">
            <div class="why-image animate-on-scroll">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1488646953014-85cb44e25828?w=600&q=80" alt="سفر وسياحة">
                <div class="experience-badge">
                    <h4>15+</h4>
                    <p>سنة من<br>الخبرة</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="why-content animate-on-scroll">
                <h2>لماذا تختار <span>نخلة بابل</span>؟</h2>
                <p>نحن لسنا مجرد وكالة سفر، نحن شريكك في صناعة ذكريات لا تُنسى. نجمع بين الخبرة العميقة والشغف بالسفر لتقديم تجربة فريدة.</p>
                <ul class="why-list">
                    <li>
                        <div class="check-icon">✓</div>
                        <div>
                            <h4>أسعار تنافسية</h4>
                            <p>نضمن لك أفضل الأسعار مع خيارات تناسب جميع الميزانيات</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <div class="check-icon">✓</div>
                        <div>
                            <h4>دعم على مدار الساعة</h4>
                            <p>فريقنا متواجد 24/7 لمساعدتك في أي وقت ومن أي مكان</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <div class="check-icon">✓</div>
                        <div>
                            <h4>برامج مخصصة</h4>
                            <p>نصمم رحلتك حسب تفضيلاتك واحتياجاتك الخاصة</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <div class="check-icon">✓</div>
                        <div>
                            <h4>شراكات عالمية</h4>
                            <p>نتعاون مع أفضل خطوط الطيران والفنادق حول العالم</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="contact" id="contact">
        <div class="contact-container">
            <div class="contact-info animate-on-scroll">
                <h2>ابدأ رحلتك <span>الآن</span></h2>
                <p>تواصل معنا للحصول على استشارة مجانية وعرض سعر مخصص لرحلتك القادمة. نحن متواجدون في بغداد وإسطنبول لخدمتك.</p>
                <div class="contact-details">
                    <div class="contact-item">
                        <div class="contact-icon">📍</div>
                        <div class="contact-text">
                            <span class="location-badge">العراق</span>
                            <h4>العنوان - بغداد</h4>
                            <p>بغداد - نفق الشرطة - مقابل مصرف بغداد - مجاور معرض الشهم للسيارات</p>
                            <a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/R28g7GzwkhCs5Lgc8" target="_blank" class="map-link">🗺️ عرض على الخريطة</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="contact-item">
                        <div class="contact-icon">📍</div>
                        <div class="contact-text">
                            <span class="location-badge">تركيا</span>
                            <h4>العنوان - إسطنبول</h4>
                            <p>تركيا - إسطنبول - يوسف باشا</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="contact-item">
                        <div class="contact-icon">📞</div>
                        <div class="contact-text">
                            <h4>أرقام الهاتف - العراق</h4>
                            <div class="phone-row">
                                <a href="tel:+9647843511140" class="phone-link">+964 784 351 1140</a>
                                <a href="https://wa.me/9647843511140" class="whatsapp-btn" target="_blank">💬 واتساب</a>
                            </div>
                            <div class="phone-row">
                                <a href="tel:+9647738884442" class="phone-link">+964 773 888 4442</a>
                                <a href="https://wa.me/9647738884442" class="whatsapp-btn" target="_blank">💬 واتساب</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="contact-item">
                        <div class="contact-icon">📞</div>
                        <div class="contact-text">
                            <h4>رقم الهاتف - تركيا</h4>
                            <div class="phone-row">
                                <a href="tel:+905538884443" class="phone-link">+90 553 888 4443</a>
                                <a href="https://wa.me/905538884443" class="whatsapp-btn" target="_blank">💬 واتساب</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="contact-item">
                        <div class="contact-icon">✉️</div>
                        <div class="contact-text">
                            <h4>البريد الإلكتروني</h4>
                            <p><a href="mailto:palm.babylon25@gmail.com" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.9);text-decoration:none;">palm.babylon25@gmail.com</a></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="contact-form animate-on-scroll" id="contactFormContainer">
                <h3>أرسل استفسارك</h3>
                <form id="contactForm">
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="fullName">الاسم الكامل</label>
                            <input type="text" id="fullName" placeholder="أدخل اسمك الكامل" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="phone">رقم الهاتف</label>
                            <input type="tel" id="phone" placeholder="أدخل رقم هاتفك" required>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>الوجهة المطلوبة</label>
                        <input type="hidden" id="destination" name="destination" required>
                        <div class="custom-select-wrapper" id="customSelectWrapper">
                            <div class="custom-select-trigger" id="customSelectTrigger">
                                <span class="trigger-text"><span class="trigger-placeholder">اختر الوجهة</span></span>
                                <span class="trigger-arrow">▼</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="custom-select-dropdown" id="customSelectDropdown">
                                <div class="custom-option" data-value="فيزا بالي" data-duration="10-15 يوم عمل" data-img="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1537996194471-e657df975ab4?w=400&q=80">
                                    <img class="option-img" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1537996194471-e657df975ab4?w=100&q=60" alt="بالي">
                                    <div class="option-info">
                                        <div class="option-name">فيزا بالي</div>
                                        <div class="option-duration">⏱ 10-15 يوم عمل</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="custom-option" data-value="فيزا قطر" data-duration="5-15 يوم عمل" data-img="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1512453979798-5ea266f8880c?w=400&q=80">
                                    <img class="option-img" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1512453979798-5ea266f8880c?w=100&q=60" alt="قطر">
                                    <div class="option-info">
                                        <div class="option-name">فيزا قطر</div>
                                        <div class="option-duration">⏱ 5-15 يوم عمل</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="custom-option" data-value="فيزا جورجيا" data-duration="10-15 يوم عمل" data-img="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1565008447742-97f6f38c985c?w=400&q=80">
                                    <img class="option-img" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1565008447742-97f6f38c985c?w=100&q=60" alt="جورجيا">
                                    <div class="option-info">
                                        <div class="option-name">فيزا جورجيا</div>
                                        <div class="option-duration">⏱ 10-15 يوم عمل</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="custom-option" data-value="موافقة مصر" data-duration="7-14 يوم عمل" data-img="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1572252009286-268acec5ca0a?w=400&q=80">
                                    <img class="option-img" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1572252009286-268acec5ca0a?w=100&q=60" alt="مصر">
                                    <div class="option-info">
                                        <div class="option-name">موافقة مصر</div>
                                        <div class="option-duration">⏱ 7-14 يوم عمل</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="custom-option" data-value="تأشيرة تايلند" data-duration="72 ساعة عمل" data-img="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1552465011-b4e21bf6e79a?w=400&q=80">
                                    <img class="option-img" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1552465011-b4e21bf6e79a?w=100&q=60" alt="تايلند">
                                    <div class="option-info">
                                        <div class="option-name">تأشيرة تايلند</div>
                                        <div class="option-duration">⏱ 72 ساعة عمل</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="custom-option" data-value="تأشيرة دبي" data-duration="72 ساعة عمل" data-img="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518684079-3c830dcef090?w=400&q=80">
                                    <img class="option-img" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518684079-3c830dcef090?w=100&q=60" alt="دبي">
                                    <div class="option-info">
                                        <div class="option-name">تأشيرة دبي</div>
                                        <div class="option-duration">⏱ 72 ساعة عمل</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="custom-option no-img" data-value="وجهة أخرى" data-duration="" data-img="">
                                    <span class="option-icon">🌍</span>
                                    <div class="option-info">
                                        <div class="option-name">وجهة أخرى</div>
                                        <div class="option-duration">حدد وجهتك في الملاحظات</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="destination-preview" id="destinationPreview">
                            <div class="preview-card">
                                <img id="previewImg" src="" alt="معاينة الوجهة">
                                <div class="preview-overlay">
                                    <span class="preview-name" id="previewName"></span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="notes">ملاحظات إضافية</label>
                        <textarea id="notes" placeholder="اكتب أي تفاصيل إضافية هنا..."></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">
                        <span>إرسال الطلب عبر واتساب</span>
                        <span>💬</span>
                    </button>
                </form>
                <div class="form-success" id="formSuccess">
                    <div class="success-icon">✅</div>
                    <h4>تم إرسال طلبك بنجاح!</h4>
                    <p>سيتم توجيهك إلى واتساب لإكمال التواصل</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="floating-whatsapp">
